<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Horizon City Builder — Level 2 | Horizon 4282</title>

<meta name="description" content="Horizon City Builder Level 2 adiciona escolas, hospitais, parques, turismo, pesquisa, universidade, aeroporto e porto ao simulador urbano Horizon 4282.">
<meta name="author" content="Roque Fernando Marcos Sousa">
<meta name="robots" content="index,follow">
<meta name="theme-color" content="#030712">

<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://f005.backblazeb2.com/file/horizon4282/fav-ico-100x100.png">

<style>
:root{
  --bg:#030712;
  --panel:rgba(8,21,38,.76);
  --line:rgba(125,211,252,.22);
  --line-strong:rgba(125,211,252,.55);
  --text:#eef6ff;
  --muted:#8ca3bd;
  --accent:#7dd3fc;
  --gold:#f5b740;

  --grass:#143f2b;
  --road:#64748b;
  --res:#2563eb;
  --com:#f97316;
  --ind:#9333ea;
  --power:#facc15;
  --water:#06b6d4;
  --school:#22c55e;
  --hospital:#ef4444;
  --park:#16a34a;
  --airport:#94a3b8;
  --port:#0ea5e9;
  --tourism:#f59e0b;
  --research:#a855f7;
  --university:#38bdf8;
}

*{box-sizing:border-box}

html,body{
  margin:0;
  min-height:100vh;
}

body{
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top left,rgba(14,165,233,.15),transparent 32%),
    radial-gradient(circle at bottom right,rgba(245,183,64,.08),transparent 34%),
    var(--bg);
  color:var(--text);
  font-family:"Courier New",monospace;
  overflow-x:hidden;
}

body::before{
  content:"";
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  pointer-events:none;
  background:
    linear-gradient(rgba(18,16,16,0) 50%,rgba(0,0,0,.20) 50%),
    linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,0,0,.03),rgba(0,255,255,.015),rgba(0,0,255,.03));
  background-size:100% 3px,3px 100%;
  opacity:.5;
  z-index:999;
}

.topbar{
  position:relative;
  z-index:2;
  min-height:74px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:space-between;
  gap:16px;
  padding:18px 28px;
  border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  background:rgba(3,7,18,.82);
  backdrop-filter:blur(18px);
}

.brand strong{
  display:block;
  color:var(--accent);
  letter-spacing:.28em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:14px;
}

.brand span{
  display:block;
  margin-top:5px;
  color:var(--muted);
  letter-spacing:.18em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:11px;
}

.top-actions{
  display:flex;
  gap:10px;
  align-items:center;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
}

.lang-btn,
.home-link,
.small-btn{
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  background:rgba(8,21,38,.55);
  color:var(--accent);
  padding:10px 14px;
  text-decoration:none;
  font-family:inherit;
  letter-spacing:.16em;
  cursor:pointer;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:12px;
}

.lang-btn.active,
.lang-btn:hover,
.home-link:hover,
.small-btn:hover{
  border-color:var(--line-strong);
  color:#fff;
  background:rgba(14,165,233,.12);
}

.page{
  position:relative;
  z-index:1;
  width:min(1660px,calc(100% - 44px));
  margin:30px auto 60px;
}

.hero{
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(8,21,38,.78),rgba(3,7,18,.78));
  padding:30px;
  margin-bottom:18px;
}

.eyebrow{
  color:var(--gold);
  letter-spacing:.26em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:12px;
  margin-bottom:12px;
}

.hero h1{
  margin:0 0 12px;
  font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,58px);
  letter-spacing:.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
}

.hero p{
  max-width:1080px;
  color:#b4c7df;
  line-height:1.7;
  font-size:16px;
}

.dashboard-bar{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(8,1fr);
  gap:12px;
  margin-bottom:18px;
}

.dash-card{
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  background:var(--panel);
  padding:13px 12px;
  text-align:center;
}

.dash-card span{
  display:block;
  color:var(--muted);
  font-size:10px;
  letter-spacing:.13em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
}

.dash-card strong{
  display:block;
  margin-top:8px;
  color:var(--gold);
  font-size:22px;
  line-height:1;
}

.game-shell{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:250px 1fr 330px;
  gap:20px;
  align-items:start;
}

.panel{
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  background:var(--panel);
  padding:18px;
}

.panel-title{
  color:var(--accent);
  letter-spacing:.22em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:12px;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}

.tools-panel{
  position:sticky;
  top:18px;
  max-height:calc(100vh - 36px);
  overflow:auto;
  scrollbar-width:thin;
  scrollbar-color:rgba(125,211,252,.25) transparent;
}

.tools-panel::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}
.tools-panel::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent}
.tools-panel::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:rgba(125,211,252,.22);border-radius:20px}

.tools{
  display:grid;
  gap:9px;
}

.tool{
  min-height:44px;
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:12px;
  border:1px solid rgba(125,211,252,.16);
  background:rgba(8,21,38,.52);
  color:var(--text);
  padding:0 12px;
  font-family:inherit;
  cursor:pointer;
  text-align:left;
}

.tool:hover,
.tool.active{
  border-color:var(--line-strong);
  background:rgba(14,165,233,.13);
  color:#fff;
}

.tool i{
  width:26px;
  text-align:center;
  font-style:normal;
}

.center{
  min-width:0;
}

.city-toolbar{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  gap:12px;
  align-items:center;
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  background:rgba(8,21,38,.55);
  padding:12px 14px;
  margin-bottom:14px;
}

#message{
  color:var(--muted);
  font-size:12px;
  letter-spacing:.12em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
}

.grid-wrap{
  border:1px solid var(--line);
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(14,165,233,.08),rgba(0,0,0,.2));
  padding:14px;
  overflow:auto;
}

#grid{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(18,38px);
  grid-template-rows:repeat(18,38px);
  gap:2px;
  width:max-content;
  margin:0 auto;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.35);
  border:1px solid rgba(125,211,252,.12);
}

.cell{
  width:38px;
  height:38px;
  background:var(--grass);
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  cursor:pointer;
  user-select:none;
  transition:.12s;
  position:relative;
  font-size:17px;
}

.cell:hover{
  filter:brightness(1.25);
  transform:scale(1.04);
  z-index:2;
}

.cell.residential{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--res),#0f172a)}
.cell.commercial{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--com),#0f172a)}
.cell.industrial{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--ind),#0f172a)}
.cell.road{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--road),#1e293b)}
.cell.power{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--power),#78350f)}
.cell.water{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--water),#083344)}
.cell.school{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--school),#052e16)}
.cell.hospital{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--hospital),#450a0a)}
.cell.park{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--park),#052e16)}
.cell.airport{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--airport),#1e293b)}
.cell.port{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--port),#082f49)}
.cell.tourism{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--tourism),#451a03)}
.cell.research{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--research),#2e1065)}
.cell.university{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--university),#083344)}

.cell.disconnected::after,
.cell.polluted::after{
  position:absolute;
  right:2px;
  top:2px;
  font-size:10px;
}

.cell.disconnected::after{content:"⚠️"}
.cell.polluted::after{content:"☣"}

.rules{
  display:grid;
  gap:10px;
  color:#b4c7df;
  line-height:1.55;
  font-size:13px;
}

.rule{
  border:1px solid rgba(125,211,252,.13);
  padding:12px;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);
}

.rule strong{
  color:var(--gold);
}

.legend{
  display:grid;
  grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
  gap:8px;
  margin-top:14px;
}

.legend-item{
  display:flex;
  align-items:center;
  gap:8px;
  color:var(--muted);
  font-size:12px;
}

.swatch{
  width:18px;
  height:18px;
  border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
}

footer{
  margin-top:30px;
  border-top:1px solid rgba(125,211,252,.14);
  padding-top:24px;
  color:var(--muted);
  text-align:center;
  font-size:12px;
  letter-spacing:.18em;
  text-transform:uppercase;
}
.modal-overlay{
  position:fixed;
  inset:0;
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.85);
  display:none;
  justify-content:center;
  align-items:center;
  z-index:5000;
}

.modal-overlay.active{
  display:flex;
}

.modal-window{
  width:min(920px,90vw);
  max-height:80vh;
  overflow:auto;
  border:1px solid var(--line-strong);
  background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(8,21,38,.96),rgba(3,7,18,.96));
  padding:24px;
}

.modal-header{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:space-between;
  align-items:center;
  margin-bottom:20px;
}

.modal-header h2{
  color:var(--accent);
  letter-spacing:.2em;
}

.modal-close{
  background:none;
  border:none;
  color:white;
  cursor:pointer;
  font-size:24px;
}

.tip-card{
  border:1px solid rgba(125,211,252,.15);
  padding:16px;
  margin-bottom:12px;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
}

.tip-card h3{
  color:var(--gold);
  margin-bottom:8px;
}

.tip-card p{
  color:#c8d6e5;
  line-height:1.6;
}

@media(max-width:1280px){
  .dashboard-bar{
    grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
  }

  .game-shell{
    grid-template-columns:250px 1fr;
  }

  .rules-panel{
    grid-column:1 / -1;
  }
}

@media(max-width:860px){
  .dashboard-bar{
    grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);
  }

  .game-shell{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
  }

  .tools-panel{
    position:relative;
    top:auto;
    max-height:none;
  }
}

@media(max-width:700px){
  .page{
    width:calc(100% - 24px);
  }

  .topbar{
    align-items:flex-start;
    flex-direction:column;
  }

  #grid{
    grid-template-columns:repeat(18,32px);
    grid-template-rows:repeat(18,32px);
  }

  .cell{
    width:32px;
    height:32px;
    font-size:14px;
  }

  .city-toolbar{
    flex-direction:column;
    align-items:flex-start;
  }
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header class="topbar">
  <div class="brand">
    <strong>Horizon 4282</strong>
    <span data-pt="Simulador Urbano Experimental · Level 2" data-en="Experimental City Simulator · Level 2">Simulador Urbano Experimental · Level 2</span>
  </div>

  <div class="top-actions">
    <button id="ptBtn" class="lang-btn" onclick="setLanguage('pt')">PT</button>
    <button id="enBtn" class="lang-btn" onclick="setLanguage('en')">EN</button>
    <a class="home-link" href="/" data-pt="Início" data-en="Home">Início</a>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="page">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow" data-pt="Experimento Interativo · Level 2" data-en="Interactive Experiment · Level 2">Experimento Interativo · Level 2</div>
    <h1>Horizon City Builder</h1>
    <p data-pt="Level 2 adiciona escolas, hospitais, parques, aeroporto, porto, turismo, pesquisa e universidade. Agora sua cidade pode seguir caminhos diferentes: industrial, sustentável, turística, tecnológica ou universitária."
       data-en="Level 2 adds schools, hospitals, parks, airport, port, tourism, research and university. Now your city can follow different paths: industrial, sustainable, touristic, technological or academic.">
      Level 2 adiciona escolas, hospitais, parques, aeroporto, porto, turismo, pesquisa e universidade. Agora sua cidade pode seguir caminhos diferentes: industrial, sustentável, turística, tecnológica ou universitária.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="dashboard-bar">
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="CAIXA" data-en="MONEY">CAIXA</span><strong>$<b id="money">1200</b></strong></div>
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="POPULAÇÃO" data-en="POPULATION">POPULAÇÃO</span><strong><b id="population">0</b></strong></div>
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="RECEITA" data-en="REVENUE">RECEITA</span><strong>$<b id="revenue">0</b></strong></div>
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="FELICIDADE" data-en="HAPPINESS">FELICIDADE</span><strong><b id="happiness">100</b>%</strong></div>
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="POLUIÇÃO" data-en="POLLUTION">POLUIÇÃO</span><strong><b id="pollution">0</b>%</strong></div>
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="EDUCAÇÃO" data-en="EDUCATION">EDUCAÇÃO</span><strong><b id="education">0</b>%</strong></div>
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="SAÚDE" data-en="HEALTH">SAÚDE</span><strong><b id="health">0</b>%</strong></div>
    <div class="dash-card"><span data-pt="CICLO" data-en="CYCLE">CICLO</span><strong><b id="cycle">0</b></strong></div>
  </section>

  <section class="game-shell">

    <aside class="panel tools-panel">
      <div class="panel-title" data-pt="Ferramentas" data-en="Tools">Ferramentas</div>

      <div class="tools">
        <button class="tool active" data-tool="grass"><i>🚜</i><span data-pt="Demolir / Grama — $10" data-en="Demolish / Grass — $10">Demolir / Grama — $10</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="road"><i>🛣️</i><span data-pt="Estrada — $20" data-en="Road — $20">Estrada — $20</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="residential"><i>🏠</i><span data-pt="Residencial — $100" data-en="Residential — $100">Residencial — $100</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="commercial"><i>🏢</i><span data-pt="Comercial — $150" data-en="Commercial — $150">Comercial — $150</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="industrial"><i>🏭</i><span data-pt="Industrial — $200" data-en="Industrial — $200">Industrial — $200</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="power"><i>⚡</i><span data-pt="Energia — $300" data-en="Power — $300">Energia — $300</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="water"><i>💧</i><span data-pt="Água — $250" data-en="Water — $250">Água — $250</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="school"><i>🏫</i><span data-pt="Escola — $350" data-en="School — $350">Escola — $350</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="hospital"><i>🏥</i><span data-pt="Hospital — $450" data-en="Hospital — $450">Hospital — $450</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="park"><i>🌳</i><span data-pt="Parque — $180" data-en="Park — $180">Parque — $180</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="airport"><i>✈️</i><span data-pt="Aeroporto — $900" data-en="Airport — $900">Aeroporto — $900</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="port"><i>🚢</i><span data-pt="Porto — $750" data-en="Port — $750">Porto — $750</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="tourism"><i>🏖️</i><span data-pt="Turismo — $400" data-en="Tourism — $400">Turismo — $400</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="research"><i>🔬</i><span data-pt="Pesquisa — $650" data-en="Research — $650">Pesquisa — $650</span></button>
        <button class="tool" data-tool="university"><i>🎓</i><span data-pt="Universidade — $800" data-en="University — $800">Universidade — $800</span></button>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <section class="center">
      <div class="city-toolbar">
        <div id="message" data-pt="Selecione uma ferramenta e clique no mapa." data-en="Select a tool and click the map.">
          Selecione uma ferramenta e clique no mapa.
        </div>

        <div class="top-actions">
          <button class="small-btn" onclick="saveGame()" data-pt="Salvar" data-en="Save">Salvar</button>
          <button class="small-btn" onclick="resetGame()" data-pt="Resetar" data-en="Reset">Resetar</button>
          <button class="small-btn" onclick="openHelpModal()" data-pt="Ajuda" data-en="Help">Ajuda</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid-wrap">
        <div id="grid"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <aside class="panel rules-panel">
      <div class="panel-title" data-pt="Regras Level 2" data-en="Level 2 Rules">Regras Level 2</div>

      <div class="rules">
        <div class="rule" data-pt="<strong>Base:</strong> estradas, energia e água continuam essenciais para ativar zonas."
             data-en="<strong>Base:</strong> roads, power and water are still essential to activate zones."><strong>Base:</strong> estradas, energia e água continuam essenciais para ativar zonas.</div>

        <div class="rule" data-pt="<strong>Serviços:</strong> escolas aumentam educação, hospitais aumentam saúde e parques melhoram felicidade."
             data-en="<strong>Services:</strong> schools increase education, hospitals increase health and parks improve happiness."><strong>Serviços:</strong> escolas aumentam educação, hospitais aumentam saúde e parques melhoram felicidade.</div>

        <div class="rule" data-pt="<strong>Economia avançada:</strong> aeroporto, porto, turismo, pesquisa e universidade ampliam a receita quando a cidade tem população suficiente."
             data-en="<strong>Advanced economy:</strong> airport, port, tourism, research and university increase revenue when the city has enough population."><strong>Economia avançada:</strong> aeroporto, porto, turismo, pesquisa e universidade ampliam a receita quando a cidade tem população suficiente.</div>

        <div class="rule" data-pt="<strong>Estratégia:</strong> uma cidade sustentável usa parques e hospitais. Uma cidade tecnológica usa pesquisa e universidade. Uma cidade turística usa aeroporto, porto e turismo."
             data-en="<strong>Strategy:</strong> a sustainable city uses parks and hospitals. A tech city uses research and university. A tourism city uses airport, port and tourism."><strong>Estratégia:</strong> uma cidade sustentável usa parques e hospitais. Uma cidade tecnológica usa pesquisa e universidade. Uma cidade turística usa aeroporto, porto e turismo.</div>
